Hastur ships NO model weights. The ONNX graphs and asset blobs are generated
locally by the user from their own gated SAM-3D-Body checkpoint (see docs/MODELS.md).
Whether the *converted* weights may be redistributed is being clarified with Meta
(opensource@meta.com).
